#%RAML 1.0 DataType
(package): Variant
type: VariantUpdateAction
(beta): true
displayName: VariantRemoveStagedChangesAction
discriminatorValue: removeStagedChanges
description: |
  Removes all staged changes from the Variant, only the current data remains.
  Generates the [VariantStagedChangesRemoved](ctp:api:type:VariantStagedChangesRemovedMessage) Message.
example: !include ../../../examples/Variant/VariantRemoveStagedChangesAction.json
